data.description: Welcome to 1072 W Northstar Drive. This beautifully updated home will bring you elegance and plenty of living space. As you enter, you will walk into an open floor plan concept offering you a newly upgraded kitchen with beautiful white cabinets, black countertops, backsplash, large kitchen island, mini fridge, gas fireplace, recessed lighting, living room, plantation shutters and laminate wood like floors throughout the home. The main bathroom and master bathroom have been upgraded with new tile showers, vanities, fixtures and sinks. Built into the ceiling of both bathroom showers are Bluetooth speakers with smart touch wall outlets to easily listen to your favorite music as you're getting ready for the day. Once you're ready to head to the back yard, you will see the amazing inground pool for those hot summer days, bonus finished storage shed with power that can easily be converted to a cute little pool house or whatever your heart desires. Not to mention gathering around the stone gas fire pit. This is a must see, there is too much to mention. All measurements are approximate, buyers should verify all information.
